{"tid":170984,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【紅Phone現】蘋果發售紅色iPhone7及7 Plus 先達Lo哥:「冇得炒」","createTime":"2017-03-25T04:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T05:44:04.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e072e9d0f0e5b8ca5e8981459901ffc339965d77","tid":170984,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T04:36:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bh03Pkp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBh03Pkp.jpg&h=cf4a9d0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘋果將於今晚11時，開售紅色版iPhone7及7 Plus ，強攻中國市場。不過，旺角先達手機舖負責人，人稱「Lo哥」的劉志剛直言，今次新色iPhone「無得炒」，更與今年推出iPhone8無關。「賣咗咁多年機，鮮色機賣出數量，不嬲比較少」他指出紅色難以針對男士市場，即使可能買新機送禮，但數量始終有限。目前，蘋果所推出5隻顏色，先達的價格已低於官方定價。他謂有中國顧客致電，但只是查詢而沒有預訂，「預期周日收機時，可能減數十至100元，下周一應該大跌，低過公價收機。」<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日前公佈發售紅色版，售價不變，介乎6,388元至8,288元，並貫上PRODUCT（RED）招牌，相關產品會為The Global Fund基金籌款，支持對抗愛滋病及HIV病毒。同時，紅色版亦甚有中國特色，明顯是針對中國市場。據中國電子商貿平台京東商城的網站顯示，截至昨晚10時半止，已有50.5萬人預約。<br />\n<br />\n記者 岑梽豪<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56475969&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56475969%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170324&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=3a7ba4fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56475969%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170324&h=bad6b7f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56475969&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170324</a><br />\n<br />\n//呢劑最少炒上2皮嘢啦，仲使諗，fatfat啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab25fc4ee4506b7ffda4ac89162ab565a14e1800","tid":170984,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T05:37:53.000Z","msg":"我想用紅色喎，係咪唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce27c69105172cb75a592bd6b139d64e04dca67","tid":170984,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T05:40:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想用紅色喎，係咪唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢紅白差啲<br />\n紅黑其實型架"},{"pid":"361f4837d9cc89bc3aeda783e2522e0421491e12","tid":170984,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T05:41:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想用紅色喎，係咪唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢紅白差啲<br />\n紅黑其實型架</blockquote><br />\n我意思如果出紅黑唔係紅白"},{"pid":"78ef3729bda8f74338af680fd23d5c1fdccb6c4a","tid":170984,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T05:42:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想用紅色喎，係咪唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢紅白差啲<br />\n紅黑其實型架</blockquote><br />\n不過無錢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd68f7ec37e83116ffbcb26be291b26e2e5dab46","tid":170984,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T05:44:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想用紅色喎，係咪唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢紅白差啲<br />\n紅黑其實型架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用黑面玻璃貼加個套"}]}